                <section id="section-evolution" class="mb-16">
                  <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">6. Qi Standard Evolution: Qi v1.0 to Qi2.2 (25W)</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">According to Counterpoint Research, over 60% of flagship smartphones shipped in 2025 support wireless charging, with Qi2 becoming the universal standard.</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Understanding the evolution of the Qi standard helps explain why cordless charging efficiency and capabilities have improved dramatically over the past decade. For a complete walkthrough of the certification process, see our <a href="/blog/qi-certification-guide" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline font-semibold">Qi Certification Guide</a>.</p>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
                        <table class="w-full text-sm">
                            <thead>
                                <tr class="bg-slate-100">
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-brandBlue">Version</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-brandBlue">Year</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-brandBlue">Max Power</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-brandBlue">Key Features</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody class="text-slate-600">
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
                                    <td class="p-4">Qi v1.0</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">2008</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">5W</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Basic inductive charging, limited interoperability</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
                                    <td class="p-4">Qi v1.1</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">2012</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">7.5W</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Improved Foreign Object Detection (FOD)</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
                                    <td class="p-4">Qi v1.2</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">2015</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">15W</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Extended Power Profile, fast charging support</td>
                                </tr>
